      <iframe src="Biodata.html" frameborder="0"></iframe> </div>
    <div class="section">
      <h3>II. CHIEF COMPLAINTS (CHRONOLOGICAL ORDER, WITH DURATION)</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>e.g., Pain in [specific joint/area] for [duration]</li>
        <li>e.g., Swelling in [specific joint/area] for [duration]</li>
        <li>e.g., Difficulty walking / using [limb] for [duration]</li>
        <li>e.g., Deformity of [area] noticed for [duration]</li>
        <li>e.g., Stiffness in [joint] for [duration]</li>
        <li>e.g., Weakness in [limb/area] for [duration]</li>
        <li>e.g., Numbness/Tingling in [area] for [duration]</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <h4>ELABORATION OF CHIEF COMPLAINT (e.g., JOINT PAIN)</h4>
      <p class="ortho-specific">(Repeat similar detailed elaboration for other
        chief complaints like swelling, stiffness, deformity, weakness etc.)</p>
